The '''Roonstones''' were extremely valuable [[Crystal/Legends|crystals]] found in the Umboo province on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Roon/Legends|Roon]]. As the maniacal [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Bisad Koong|Koong]] deliberately destroyed the only known cache of roonstones, and the other set was thrown into the [[Roon Sea]], it was presumed that the only surviving gems was the one on display in the [[Baobab Archives]] and the one [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Terrinald Screed/Legends|Terrinald Screed]] gave to the [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]].

The stone in the archives was retrieved by the intrepid explorer [[Mungo Baobab]], who set off to find the stones with his [[Droid/Legends|droid]] companions, [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] and [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]]. This particular gem was encoded with the ''[[Dha Werda Verda]]'', an epic poem of the conquest of the [[Zhell/Legends|Zhell]], indigenous people of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] who may have been the ancestors of the [[Human/Legends|Human race]], by a warrior race called the [[Taung/Legends|Taungs]], who later became the [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorians]].

[[Kessum]] was a type of Roonstone.

